ul.li:
Guess - displays a list of words suggested to replace the unknown
        word. Double click a word to automatically insert it in the document and resume the spell
        checking process;

Replace All - replaces all occurrences of the currently highlighted
        word in the XML document, with the selected word in the Replace with
        field;

Ignore - ignores the first occurrence of the unrecognized word and
        allows you to continue checking the document.  skips the content of the
        XML elements marked as ignorable;
